	   <tr><td colspan=2>Karg Icebear is a wandering merchant.  Martar Icebear is his evil brother who is KOS for EVERYbody.  They will fight each other if they meet and Tundra Jack will also fight Martar if they meet.  Karg AND Martar are both level 35 and thats a fact.  (By the way I know that Tundra Jack attacks Martar because Martar jumped me and 70! 70! 50! 70! at that point I was almost dead and lived only due to the picks of Jack.)  Karg drops a Cloak of an Icebear (common) and a Gigantic Zwiendhander (rare).  He is for the quest for a Polar Bear Cloak, Lupine Claw Gauntlets, and a Werewolf Hide Cloak.  Karg is NOT a rare spawn however he IS hard to find due to the fact that he roams around the tundra part of Everfrost.  He will not help you if you are in trouble so if you run into him with an Ice Giant running after you don't think its your lucky day.  Oh and he doesn't have some "special" cold resistance.  Karg has the same stats as any other Barbarian.  I hope THAT clears some things up, other experienced players can verify my FACTS.<br>/bow<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
